<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, minimum-scale=1">
  <title>{% block title %}KOUBO WATCH{% endblock %}</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* --- Design tokens (grid-news / egc-watch style) --- */
    :root {
      --paper: #f5f0e8;
      --ink:   #1a1a2e;
      --muted: #5a5a6e;
      --accent: #1a3a6e;
      --rule:  #b8a98a;
      --card-bg: #faf7f2;
      --card-border: #d4c9b0;
      --radius: 4px;
      --font-serif: "Noto Serif JP", "Yu Mincho", "游明朝", Georgia, serif;
      --score-high: #c0392b;
      --score-mid:  #e67e22;
      --score-low:  #7f8c8d;
      --deadline-urgent: #c0392b;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      background: var(--paper);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      min-width: 320px;
    }

    /* --- Masthead --- */
    header.masthead {
      border-bottom: 4px double var(--accent);
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    header.masthead h1 {
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      color: var(--accent);
    }
    header.masthead p.tagline {
      font-size: .85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: .25rem;
    }
    header.masthead nav.site-nav {
      margin-top: .6rem;
      font-size: .85rem;
    }
    header.masthead nav.site-nav a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 .5rem;
    }
    header.masthead nav.site-nav a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* --- Main layout --- */
    main {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem 3rem;
    }

    /* --- Badges --- */
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      border-radius: 3px;
      padding: .15em .5em;
      font-size: .78rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.4;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .badge-score-high { background: var(--score-high); color: #fff; }
    .badge-score-mid  { background: var(--score-mid);  color: #fff; }
    .badge-score-low  { background: #ccc;              color: #333; }
    .badge-deadline        { background: var(--deadline-urgent); color: #fff; }
    .badge-deadline-ok     { background: #27ae60; color: #fff; }
    .badge-deadline-passed { background: #95a5a6; color: #fff; }
    .badge-research   { background: #2980b9; color: #fff; }
    .badge-cat        { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }

    /* --- Category tags --- */
    .category-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .35rem; margin-top: .4rem; }

    /* --- Empty state --- */
    .empty {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    /* --- Footer --- */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: .8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      padding: 1rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }
    footer a { color: var(--accent); }

    /* --- Mobile --- */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      header.masthead h1 { font-size: 1.3rem; }
      main { padding: 1rem .75rem 2rem; }
    }
  </style>
  {% block extra_style %}{% endblock %}
</head>
<body>

<header class="masthead">
  <h1>KOUBO WATCH</h1>
  <p class="tagline">官公庁公募案件 — エネルギーシステム改善モニター</p>
  <nav class="site-nav">
    <a href="index.html">最新案件</a>
    <a href="archive.html">アーカイブ</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<main>
{% block content %}{% endblock %}
</main>

<footer>
  KOUBO WATCH — 自動生成サイト。原典は各府省庁公式サイトを参照してください。
  生成日時: {% block generated_at %}—{% endblock %}
</footer>

</body>
</html>
